# Prisma Rules

- Schema lives at `prisma/schema.prisma`.
- Follow Ghostfolio's existing model naming conventions (PascalCase models,
  camelCase fields).
- New agent-related models should be prefixed or grouped clearly
  (e.g., `AgentConversation`, `AgentTrace`).
- Always run `npx prisma generate` after schema changes.
- Use Prisma migrations (`npx prisma migrate dev`) — never modify the database
  directly.
- Read the existing schema before adding new models to avoid duplication.
